dsDescriptionValue.value: PharmacoMEG data from Muthukumaraswamy and Liley 2018. NeuroImage. "1/f electrophysiological spectra in resting and drug-induced states can be explained by the dynamics of multiple oscillatory relaxation processes"

fields.value:
Data are described in Table S1 in the paper. File naming here is as follows
$STUDY_$SESSION_$SUBJECTID

$STUDY = PMP (perampanel) or KET (ketamine) or LSD or TGB (tiagabine)
$SESSION = One of the four above or PLA
$SUBJECTID = Numerical code for each participant

As all studies were crossover there will be pairs of data sets e.g.
PMP_PLA_240107_6
PMP_PMP_240107_6
are the placebo and perampanel sessions from the perampanel study for a single participant
